    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Architecture that focuses on the design, renovation, and remodeling of golf courses, which are large outdoor areas where the sport of golf is played, consisting of a teeing ground, fairway, rough, hazards, and a series of greens.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
